data_table.description: Data contain extensive medical history information of subjects (all > 65 years of age), describing general physical health, including results of bloodwork, ECG and use of medications/multivitamins and subjects' mobility/independence and movement limitations. Lifestyle information is provided through variables querying for dietary habits and alcohol consumption. Data were collected at baseline (2).
